strings:
<voice_0x01001677><center>My beloved kin.
<center>We sages have done all that we can...

<voice_0x01001678><center>Now our dear world, our future,
<center>lies in your hands. Protect it well...

<voice_0x01001679><center>We will be watching you.
<center>Farewell, my beloved kin.
<center>Farewell, Empyrea...

<voice_0x0100167B><se_low><center>Meddling pests!
<center>How much more of my time will you waste!?

<voice_0x0100167C><se_low><center>You will rot in hell for breaking my shield
<center>of darkness! But first you will taste the
<center>true might of my flesh and blood!

<voice_0x0100167D><se_low><center>You shall taste the terror eternal.
<center>Even death shall offer you no respite.
